- `key_double_integral_pos`: TRACKED — 1 sorry (sorry_p_B2_double_integral)
- `centroid_ineq_via_double_integral`: TRACKED — 1 sorry (sorry_p_B2_identity)
- Definitions (`area`, `x₁`, `area_rot`, `x₂`, `key_double_integral`): REAL
- Sorry count: 2 (sorry_p_B2_double_integral, sorry_p_B2_identity)
-/

end Lutar.Putnam.P_B2
